<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Warlord Realm | Server Shutdown</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/asset/logo-min.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./asset/style-shutdown_pange.css">
    <meta name="description" content="Warlord Realm Minecraft Server - Temporarily Shutdown">
</head>
<body>

<!-- Falling pixel particles -->
<div id="particles"></div>

<div class="container">

    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <div class="logo-placeholder"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i></div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="logo-text">Warlord Realm</h1>
        <p class="server-name">Minecraft Server — Java &amp; Bedrock</p>
    </header>

    <div class="status-badge">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        Server Temporarily Offline
    </div>

    <!-- Main announcement card -->
    <div class="shutdown-card">
        <div class="card-eyebrow">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
            Official Announcement
        </div>
        <h2 class="card-title">The Server is on Pause 🗡️</h2>
        <div class="message-body">
            <p>Hello guys, <span class="highlight">dipta14</span> here.</p>
            <br>
            <p>
                With a heavy heart, we have to temporarily shut down the server due to
                <span class="highlight">operational cost issues</span>. This wasn't an easy decision,
                but it's something we need to do for now.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                The server is <span class="highlight">not gone forever</span> — it's just on pause.
                We'll be back, but we can't promise when yet.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                Thank you so much to everyone who played, supported, and became part of this server.
                <span class="highlight">See you again in the future.</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature">
            <div class="sig-avatar"><img src="./asset/dipta14_pfp.png" alt="admin/founder profile picture" width="42px" height="42px" style="border-radius: 50%;"></div>
            <div>
                <div class="sig-name">dipta14</div>
                <div class="sig-role">Founder &amp; Admin — Warlord Realm</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info cards -->
    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon"><i class="fas fa-pause-circle"></i></div>
            <h3>Status</h3>
            <p>The server is temporarily paused, not deleted. All data and progress are safe.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon"><i class="fas fa-redo"></i></div>
            <h3>Will It Return?</h3>
            <p>Yes. We plan to come back when conditions allow. No ETA yet — stay tuned.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i></div>
            <h3>Stay Connected</h3>
            <p>Join our Discord to get notified the moment the server comes back online.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>See you on the other side.</p>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="./discord" target="_blank" class="footer-link">
                <i class="fab fa-discord"></i> Discord
            </a>
            <!-- <a href="./status" class="footer-link">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i> Status
            </a>
            <a href="./help/" class="footer-link">
                <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Help
            </a> -->
        </div>
    </footer>

</div>

<script src="./asset/java_script-shutdown_pange.js"></script>
</body>
</html>